<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 17:14:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>实现更便宜、更清洁的氢气生产</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/toward-cheaper-cleaner-hydrogen-production</link><description>索贝克在阿根廷出生和长大，但他也在麻省理工学院成长了三个学位和十多年的时间。他首先在麻省理工学院学习航空航天，然后作为研究生跳入机械工程，然后转到电气工程和计算机科学系，在博士生导师、麻省理工学院教授 Martha Gray 和 Stephen Senturia 的指导下工作。他的论文重点研究了一种快速测量大量生物细胞光学特性的技术。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/toward-cheaper-cleaner-hydrogen-production.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 17:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/toward-cheaper-cleaner-hydrogen-production</guid></item><item><title>JWST 在早期宇宙中发现了一个打破所有规则的恒星棒</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/jwst-finds-a-stellar-bar-in-the-early-universe-that-breaks-all-rules</link><description>天文学家使用詹姆斯·韦伯太空望远镜 (JWST) 在 GN20 中发现了一个恒星棒，GN20 是大爆炸后仅 15 亿年的巨大星系。这&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/jwst-finds-a-stellar-bar-in-the-early-universe-that-breaks-all-rules2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 16:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/jwst-finds-a-stellar-bar-in-the-early-universe-that-breaks-all-rules</guid></item><item><title>童年时期不规则的大脑成熟预示着青春期早期的情绪习惯</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/irregular-brain-maturation-in-childhood-predicts-emotional-habits-in-early-adolescence</link><description>一项新的研究表明，儿童大脑成熟的速度可以预测他们在青少年时期是否倾向于压抑自己的情绪，这为了解青少年心理健康的生物学根源提供了新的线索。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/irregular-brain-maturation-in-childhood-predicts-emotional-habits-in-early-adolescence.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 16:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/irregular-brain-maturation-in-childhood-predicts-emotional-habits-in-early-adolescence</guid></item><item><title>量子互联网，解释</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-quantum-internet-explained</link><description>量子互联网是一个由量子计算机组成的网络，有一天它将发送、计算和接收以量子态编码的信息。量子互联网不会取代现代或“经典”互联网；相反，它将提供量子密码学和量子云计算等新功能。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-quantum-internet-explained.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 16:29:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-quantum-internet-explained</guid></item><item><title>Microcombs 为 6G 解锁 560GHz 112Gbps 无线链路</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/microcombs-unlock-112gbps-wireless-link-at-560ghz-for-6g</link><description>德岛大学的研究人员展示了使用孤子微梳在 560 GHz 频段实现 112 Gbps 的单通道无线传输，标志着向下一代 6G 通信迈出了重要一步。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/microcombs-unlock-112gbps-wireless-link-at-560ghz-for-6g2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 16:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/microcombs-unlock-112gbps-wireless-link-at-560ghz-for-6g</guid></item><item><title>哈佛大学为公众发布长寿报告</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/harvard-publishes-a-longevity-report-for-the-general-public</link><description>这份题为《长寿之道》的报告向普通读者介绍了几个重要的长寿概念， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/harvard-publishes-a-longevity-report-for-the-general-public.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 15:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/harvard-publishes-a-longevity-report-for-the-general-public</guid></item><item><title>Anthropic 首席执行官 Dario Amodei 谈论扩展法律、人工智能军备竞赛和激进的丰富性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/anthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-talks-scaling-laws-ai-arms-races-and-radical-abundance</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 15:44:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/anthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-talks-scaling-laws-ai-arms-races-and-radical-abundance</guid></item><item><title>太阳能海水淡化系统将海水转化为饮用水，不产生浪费</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/solar-powered-desalination-system-turns-ocean-water-into-drinking-water-without-waste</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 15:29:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/solar-powered-desalination-system-turns-ocean-water-into-drinking-water-without-waste</guid></item><item><title>研究人员阻断有助于帕金森病在大脑中传播的关键蛋白质</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/researchers-block-key-protein-that-helps-parkinsons-spread-through-the-brain</link><description>一种新发现的名为 GPNMB 的蛋白质可能在帮助帕金森病在大脑中传播方面发挥重要作用。研究人员发现，免疫细胞会释放这种蛋白质来响应受损的神经元，从而形成恶性循环，加速脑细胞退化。在早期实验中，阻断 GPNMB 的抗体阻止了毒性过程在细胞之间传播。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-block-key-protein-that-helps-parkinsons-spread-through-the-brain.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 15:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/researchers-block-key-protein-that-helps-parkinsons-spread-through-the-brain</guid></item><item><title>牛津实验室内部将建造英国的下一代量子机器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/inside-the-oxford-lab-set-to-build-the-uks-next-quantum-machines</link><description>英国第一台 100 量子位量子计算机和经过潜艇测试的原子钟现已落户 Infleqtion 的新牛津中心，使当地研发和生产增加了两倍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/inside-the-oxford-lab-set-to-build-the-uks-next-quantum-machines.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 14:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/inside-the-oxford-lab-set-to-build-the-uks-next-quantum-machines</guid></item></channel></rss>